            <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4 7 9 12 16 17</NUMEX> ] . <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CMV</ENAMEX> colitis cases were excluded
            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">morphologically</ENAMEX> based on the presence of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CMV</ENAMEX> cytopathic
            effect or CMV immunohistochemistry. The cases with
            suspicious features such as ill defined cytopathic
